    "body" : "<p>There is no difference in behavior that I can find between the two (other than the obvious null-case). As for which version to prefer, I would go with the second. It is the standard way of doing this in Java.</p>\n\n<p>If it confuses readers of your code (because <code>String[] instanceof Object[]</code> is true), you may want to use the first to be more explicit if code reviewers keep asking about it.</p>\n"
