    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p><code>getClass().isArray()</code> is significantly slower on Sun Java 5 or 6 JRE than on IBM.</p>\n\n<p>So much that using <code>clazz.getName().charAt(0) == '['</code> is faster on Sun JVM.</p>\n"
